{"prompt": "Generate a website for a cybersecurity firm. The website should be secure and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SecureShield Cybersecurity</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #0a2342; /* Deep Blue */\n            --secondary-color: #24537d; /* Lighter Blue */\n            --text-color: #f0f0f0; /* Light Gray for contrast */\n            --accent-color: #d4af37; /* Gold accent */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        main {\n            padding: 2rem 1rem;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            font-size: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        p {\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            color: #cccccc;\n        }\n\n        .service-list {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 25px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            width: 300px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1.5rem 0;\n            margin-top: 3rem;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #c19e32; /* Slightly darker gold */\n            color: #051121; /* Darker primary for hover */\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 4rem 1rem;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3rem;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .security-icon {\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .animated-text {\n            animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in-out;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes fadeIn {\n            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }\n            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>SecureShield Cybersecurity</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"animated-text\">\n            <h2>Your Digital Fortress in a Complex World</h2>\n            <p>Protecting your assets with cutting-edge security solutions.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get a Free Consultation</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <main>\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>SecureShield Cybersecurity is dedicated to providing robust and innovative security services to businesses of all sizes. We understand the ever-evolving threat landscape and equip you with the defenses needed to thrive securely.</p>\n            <p>Our team of expert analysts and ethical hackers works tirelessly to identify vulnerabilities, mitigate risks, and ensure the integrity of your digital operations.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"services\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <ul class=\"service-list\">\n                <li class=\"service-item\">\n                    <div class=\"security-icon\">\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f</div>\n                    <h3>Vulnerability Assessment</h3>\n                    <p>Proactive identification and analysis of weaknesses in your systems.</p>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"service-item\">\n                    <div class=\"security-icon\">\ud83d\udd12</div>\n                    <h3>Penetration Testing</h3>\n                    <p>Simulating real-world attacks to test your defenses.</p>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"service-item\">\n                    <div class=\"security-icon\">\ud83d\udcca</div>\n                    <h3>Security Auditing</h3>\n                    <p>Comprehensive review of your security policies and procedures.</p>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"service-item\">\n                    <div class=\"security-icon\">\ud83d\udea8</div>\n                    <h3>Incident Response</h3>\n                    <p>Rapid and effective containment and remediation of security breaches.</p>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"service-item\">\n                    <div class=\"security-icon\">\u2601\ufe0f</div>\n                    <h3>Cloud Security</h3>\n                    <p>Securing your cloud infrastructure and data.</p>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"service-item\">\n                    <div class=\"security-icon\">\ud83d\udc68\u200d\ud83d\udcbb</div>\n                    <h3>Security Awareness Training</h3>\n                    <p>Educating your staff to be the first line of defense.</p>\n                </li>\n            </ul>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Let's Secure Your Future</h2>\n            <p>Ready to strengthen your cybersecurity posture? Contact us today for a personalized assessment and tailored solutions.</p>\n            <a href=\"mailto:info@secureshield.com\" class=\"cta-button\">Contact Us</a>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 SecureShield Cybersecurity. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n            const heroHeading = document.querySelector('.hero h2');\n            if (heroHeading) {\n                heroHeading.classList.add('animated-text');\n            }\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}